       Name: Beacon
    Classes: Mage(70), Psionicist(70)
   Duration: 20 + ( Cast Level / 3 )
   Modifies: N/A
       Type: N/A
Description: A beacon allows you to create a magical beacon which you name
             allowing you to eventually (when you get the portal spell)
             create a portal or gateway to the room in which you left the
             beacon. IE: c beacon bread will create a magical beacon named
             bread.
